text:
WATCH: Dude Gets Catfish By A Chick He Met Online And Humiliates Her! 1 hour ago share 
"In 2017, you would think everyone would be aware of the risk involved with online dating. Apparently, this dude didn't get the memo about catfishing. Once he realizes he's been catfished, the man goes in on the chick clowning her weight and how she isn't the woman in the photo! Let his experience be your warning. Watch below!" SOURCE Qui West began his radio journey in 2006 as an intern in San Francisco where he developed a love for radio. From there, he became a public affairs host and landed a weekend on air spot with KYLD Wild 949. The he hit the majors and worked at Houston's legendary hip hop station KBXX 979 The Box. Qui West hosted the No.1 rated night show in the market for almost 4 years. Most recently, he was home in San Francisco at KRBQ 102. Now he has a new home, right here in the I.E. on 99.1 KGGI. Join him every afternoon from 2-6p and follow him everywhere @QuiWest. Contact
